Package entity

Class ResourceNodeEntityId

java.lang.Object
entity.ResourceNodeEntityId
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ResourceNodeEntityId extends Object implements Serializable
Identifier class for the ResourceNodeEntity entity. This class defines a composite primary key used in the "resource_node" table. The composite key consists of the `countryId` and `resourceId` fields.

Implements Serializable as required for composite key classes in JPA.
